node.text:
The new BUGATTI smartwatch range, created with VIITA Watches, mirrors the unrivalled precision, artistry and technology synonymous with hyper sports cars crafted in Molsheim. Each of the models offers an innumerable amount of technical features and is built by hand with meticulous attention to detail for a seamless integration of more than 1,000 individual parts. Discover the collection at www.bugatti.com or www.bugatti-smartwatches.com. @bugatti_smartwatches

He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

BUGATTI‘s “La Maison Pur Sang” program is the ultimate seal of authenticity for all past, present and future examples of our marque‘s hyper sports cars.

Models from BUGATTI‘s illustrious history will undergo an extensive certification process at the home of BUGATTI in Mosheim, France. The program also offers customers and collectors an intensive range of restoration and reconfiguration options. 

The very first model to receive “La Maison Pur Sang” certification of authenticity is a stunning 2008 VEYRON 16.4 Grand Sport, which has been meticulously restored to its launch specification by the Molsheim team of experts over a period of four months. 

#BUGATTI #LaMaisonPurSang #VEYRON #VEYRONGrandSport #GrandSport

With the DIVO, coachbuilding reached the modern era. As BUGATTI‘s first contemporary coachbuilt hyper sports car, the DIVO exemplifies all of our marque‘s groundbreaking prowess, with unprecedented levels of hand-crafted detail. 
The entire interior layout is completely focused on the driver. The seats offer great lateral support with the lightweight central console, giving additional support thanks to larger armrests and calf supports.

Bon 14 Juillet à toutes et à tous. Vive la République, vive la France! For over a century, BUGATTI and France have flourished in unison. Today, BUGATTI honors and celebrates the Grande Nation’s history and values with a special tribute.

From the marque’s very first car - the BUGATTI Type 13 - handcrafted in the early 20th century, to launching the sector-defining CHIRON in 2016, BUGATTI and France are synonymous with savoir vivre – a lifestyle that attracted and shaped Ettore Bugatti and which is reflected in our vehicles up to this day.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #CHIRON #14Juillet #FeteNationale #QuatorzeJuillet #ViveLaFrance #BastilleDay

More than 110 years ago in 1909, Ettore Bugatti chose Molsheim in Alsace, France, to be the home of the marque that is now so intrinsically linked with the country and its shared values. 

This year, BUGATTI pays homage to the Grande Nation for the Fête Nationale with an exceptional tricolore with three CHIRON – each uniquely colored in blue, white, and red – symbolizing our French origins and haute couture of the automotive industry. Bon 14 Juillet à toutes et à tous. Vive la République, vive la France!

A star on four wheels generating as much attention as Hollywood celebrities. It’s BUGATTI’s CHIRON Sport “Les Légendes du Ciel” on Cannes’ famous La Croisette, where BUGATTI partner and Paris dealer Groupe Schumacher @bugatti_paris held an exclusive dinner.

The Cannes Film Festival is celebrating its 74th edition this year and has long become a must see. It stands for what France and the French stand for: elegance, exclusivity, eccentricity, and creativity. It is therefore the perfect event for our CHIRON to present its looks and skills. @festivaldecannes
